peopleAlsoAsk.question: How to tell how old cufflinks are?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: You can estimate the age of cufflinks by looking at their design, materials and any markings or hallmarks. Vintage cufflinks may have styles that were popular in the past, like Art Deco or Victorian designs. Check for any dates or maker's marks on them as these can provide clues about their age.
